  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下 Gafaelfawr 的登录流程。用户从浏览器访问服务，先经过 ingress，然后 Gafaelfawr 做认证子请求。如果还没登录，应该返回 401，然后重定向到登录页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser",
        "ingress",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "401",
        "/login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以 ingress 收到 401 之后，是直接把浏览器重定向到 /login，还是先到 Gafaelfawr 再到登录页？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ingress",
        "browser",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "/login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "浏览器访问 /login 的时候，请求还是要经过 ingress 再到 Gafaelfawr，然后 Gafaelfawr 把用户重定向到外部的 provider 去做真正的身份认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser",
        "ingress",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "provider",
        "/login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这条链路加上：浏览器到 ingress，再到 Gafaelfawr，然后重定向到 provider。provider 认证完成后，再跳回 /login。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser",
        "ingress",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "provider",
        "/login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，然后 Gafaelfawr 会向 provider 请求 token，拿到 token 之后，再告诉 ingress 重定向回原来的 service。这时候浏览器重新访问 service URL，Gafaelfawr 这次返回 200，ingress 才能把请求转发给后端 service。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "provider",
        "token",
        "ingress",
        "service",
        "200",
        "service URL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，第二次访问 service URL 的时候，ingress 还是要发 auth subrequest 给 Gafaelfawr 对吧？只是这次返回 200 而不是 401。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ingress",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "auth subrequest",
        "200",
        "service URL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，两次 auth subrequest 的流程要画完整。最后 service 返回 response，经过 ingress 回到浏览器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "service",
        "ingress",
        "browser",
        "response",
        "auth subrequest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我画了两轮完整的交互：第一轮未认证走 401 和登录流程，第二轮已认证走 200 到 service，最后返回响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser",
        "ingress",
        "Gafaelfawr",
        "service",
        "401",
        "200",
        "response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
